textContent:
---sadboi---

Babycakes I miss u so much!!!! Sad boy nako pota. Naiiyak nako HAHAHAHA three days tayong di magkikita niyan grabe. Day 1 of 3 palang, sobrang hirap na. Parang may ache sa chest ko na ewan huhuhu. Miss na miss na miss ko na best girl ko T.T. 

natatawa nalang ako kase ang OA ko pero buset bakit ba huhuhu. I love you sososo much my bby. Wag na wag mo ko iiwan huhu. Iiyak ako malala. Gagawa ako eksena. BWAHAHAHAHHAA


---friends---

You've introduced me to some of your friends last weekend, and they were really really hilarious!!! They look really fun to be with bby and I'm excited to meet them na! Hahaha. Of course, di parin nawawala yung part na kabado ako (duh), pero you help a lot bby!! I really do appreciate your efforts of making me feel included with your friends! I really am lucky to be with you!!! By the time na nabasa nito, sana nakita ko na nga sila in person!! 

P.s. seryoso tho, yung mga cringe mo na kaibigan/jowa ng kaibigan, ayaw ko ng makita chz HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA pero pls pag nakita ko na sila bby, gets mo naman pag nanahimik nako diba HAHAHAHAHA i have few friends for a reason. I protect my peace hahaha

---energy source---

Today was a really really bad day in terms of work (its 11:52 pm and kakatapos ko lang halos sa trabaho). Apaka tiring and draining and omg i feel so sad na kase miss na miss kita talaga and antagal pa bago kita makita ulit. What's worse is that I know na ma-hug lang kita, masosolve lahat ng energy issues ko HAHAHAHA. Good thing naman yon ket papano tho. Sign yon na love na love na love kita HAHAHAH. Haaay Rei. You really made me into a different person ðŸ¥¹ðŸ¥¹ðŸ¥¹. I love you so much!!
